        private void updateUser​(org.json.JSONObject currUser,
                        java.lang.String firstName,
                        java.lang.String lastName,
                        java.lang.String email,
                        java.lang.String password)
        Updates the user information. The information to be updated is specified by the parameters passed to the method.
        Parameters:
        currUser - The JSON object containing the current user information
        firstName - The first name of the user to be updated
        lastName - The last name of the user to be updated
        email - The email address of the user to be updated
        password - The password of the user to be updated
